action.description: Report adopted; referred to the committee(s) on EDN as amended in HD 1 with Representative(s) Cochran, Kila, Lamosao, Matsumoto, Reyes Oda, Shimizu voting aye with reservations; Representative(s) Alcos, Garcia, Kong, Muraoka, Pierick voting no (5) and Representative(s) Garrett, Holt, Keohokapu-Lee Loy, Ward excused (4).
